casebody.data:
Eric Orlando FOWLER, Appellant/Petitioner(s),
v.
STATE of Florida, Appellee/Respondent(s). CASE NO.: 2D18-4059 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Second District. October 17, 2018

BY ORDER OF THE COURT:

Petitioner's petition for writ of prohibition is denied. Petitioner's motion to stay the proceedings in the trial court is denied as moot.

KHOUZAM, MORRIS, and BADALAMENTI, JJ., Concur.
